column2: Inflation factors and discount rate from 2011 FEMP;  Regulatory surcharge is now correctly modeled as a % for gas utilities and a $/kWh surcharge for electric utilities. Jan 2022 RCC rates - fuel costs use price before taxes added as program now does the math   PCE 100% funding in effect Jan 2019. PCE kWH limited raised to 750 from 500 kWH July 2022.
